column5: This year we will experience 4 unusual dates.... 1/1/11, 1/11/11, 11/1/11, 11/11/11 .........  NOW go figure this out.... take the last 2 digits of the year you were born  plus the age you will be this year and it WILL EQUAL .... 111.
UNBELIEVABLE    That's really freaky dude I'm stunned Leechman
kinda kewl eh ....this will NEVER happen for the number 13...unless the devise a new "metric" calendar to eliminate leap year out of the equation
Kewl.... No.... fascinating     Live long and prosper!!!
hey this freaks me out man.
lol..glad i could partake in your meltdown Paul...
07/07/07 was an epic birthday for me...and for all the worlds casinos. People went nuts thinking it was lucky day
What a coincidence......111 is the number of beers I'll drink each month....freeky
